Bubble → Biggest goes last

Selection → Pick minimum

Insertion → Cards in hand

Merge → Divide & merge

Quick → Pivot based split


Sort	    Best Time	  Avg Time	  Worst Time	Space	            Stable	   In-Place	 Best Use Case
Bubble	  O(n)	      O(n²)	      O(n²)	      O(1)	             Yes	        Yes	    Nearly sorted
Selection	O(n²)   	  O(n²)	      O(n²)	      O(1)	              No	        Yes	    Less swaps
Insertion	O(n)	      O(n²)	      O(n²)	      O(1)	              Yes	        Yes	    Nearly sorted
Merge	    O(n log n)	O(n log n)	O(n log n)	O(n)	              Yes	        No	    Large data
Quick	    O(n log n)	O(n log n)	O(n²)	      O(log n)/worst-O(N)	 No	        Yes	    Fast average
